<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الذَّارِيَات<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٣٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم , وَالذَّارِيَاتِ ذَرْوًا <span class="c2">(١)</span>} <span class="c4">[الذاريات: ١]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ السَّلاَمُ:</span> <span class="c1">" الذَّارِيَاتُ: الرِّيَاحُ "</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَذْرُوهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[الكهف: ٤٥]</span>: <span class="c2">«تُفَرِّقُهُ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>